WEBVTT

00:07.090 --> 00:09.510
(Cui's Residence)

00:10.080 --> 00:11.460
Since you've decided,

00:13.210 --> 00:14.860
I'll let you do what you want.

00:15.560 --> 00:17.180
Your mother said

00:17.840 --> 00:20.190
there was no right or wrong
when it came to choices.

00:20.640 --> 00:22.270
If it was sincerely what you wanted

00:22.370 --> 00:23.750
and a decision you wouldn't regret,

00:23.970 --> 00:25.620
she would surely support you.

00:26.800 --> 00:29.870
She also never regretted
marrying your father.

00:30.680 --> 00:32.550
Guqiu's spirit

00:32.680 --> 00:35.020
will be happier than I do

00:35.430 --> 00:37.270
if she knows
you've found a suitable husband.

00:38.170 --> 00:39.420
Thanks to her,

00:39.970 --> 00:41.529
my career as an official

00:41.530 --> 00:42.940
has been smooth sailing.

00:43.320 --> 00:45.529
I prepared 12 boxes of jewellery

00:45.530 --> 00:46.740
for your dowry.

00:46.830 --> 00:48.230
I won't let you embarrass yourself.

00:48.570 --> 00:49.609
Uncle,

00:49.610 --> 00:51.380
I have enough dowry.

00:51.390 --> 00:53.840
Diannan is a poor place
and it's tough being an official here.

00:53.850 --> 00:56.039
You should leave it to Zhangru.

00:56.040 --> 00:57.609
It's for you.

00:57.610 --> 00:59.230
I have another batch prepared for Ru.

00:59.750 --> 01:01.709
I'm fully prepared.

01:01.710 --> 01:03.739
I bought a four-room house
that's facing South

01:03.740 --> 01:05.930
in the Capital.

01:06.050 --> 01:07.349
I'm just waiting to retire

01:07.350 --> 01:08.730
and reunite with the family.

01:11.690 --> 01:12.830
Father!

01:13.350 --> 01:14.490
Ru!

01:14.950 --> 01:16.210
- Ru!
- You are back!

01:18.910 --> 01:20.909
Ms. Longevity is getting married.

01:20.910 --> 01:23.050
Why haven't you found a husband?

01:23.190 --> 01:24.850
If you keep dragging this,

01:24.870 --> 01:26.680
you'll become an old single woman.

01:26.690 --> 01:27.839
Come back to Diannan with me.

01:27.840 --> 01:29.000
I'll find a husband for you.

01:29.110 --> 01:30.069
If you keep looking,

01:30.070 --> 01:32.330
I'll have buddies all over the place.

01:32.470 --> 01:34.069
- Look...
- You are retiring soon.

01:34.070 --> 01:35.709
Let's find one after you come back.

01:35.710 --> 01:36.850
All right?

01:37.390 --> 01:38.530
What's wrong?

01:39.110 --> 01:40.250
What's wrong?

01:40.790 --> 01:43.370
It's all thanks to
Zhao's husband's subordinates.

01:44.110 --> 01:48.109
He was afraid that someone
might threaten the manor

01:48.110 --> 01:50.109
and mistook me for the bad man.

01:50.110 --> 01:52.090
Do I look like a bad person?

01:53.390 --> 01:54.530
A little.

01:55.270 --> 01:56.349
My heart...

01:56.350 --> 01:57.589
Be careful.

01:57.590 --> 01:58.469
My arm.

01:58.470 --> 02:00.610
- Where did you hurt yourself?
- Everywhere.

02:00.630 --> 02:01.890
Here and here.

02:02.430 --> 02:04.490
(Uncle was supposed
to be a minor official)

02:04.710 --> 02:06.330
(who was suppressed all the time.)

02:06.390 --> 02:07.629
- (When I get married,)
-Here.

02:07.630 --> 02:10.050
(he couldn't rest
and attend the wedding.)

02:10.070 --> 02:12.740
- Father, you've worked hard.
- (His career is progressing well now)

02:12.750 --> 02:14.210
(and he is reunited with his family.)

02:14.750 --> 02:15.890
(That's great.)

02:16.740 --> 02:17.599
Understand?

02:17.600 --> 02:19.110
All right. Get married early.

02:29.750 --> 02:30.890
Your Lordship.

02:31.270 --> 02:32.180
How is it?

02:32.190 --> 02:34.130
We've dug up
the Eastern and Western mountains,

02:34.140 --> 02:35.570
but we still can't find anything.

02:35.870 --> 02:37.149
There were a few floods here.

02:37.150 --> 02:38.389
Even if it weren't destroyed,

02:38.390 --> 02:40.189
it would've been moved.

02:40.190 --> 02:42.960
Trying to find it in one night
is like finding a needle in a haystack.

02:43.660 --> 02:44.810
Keep digging.

02:45.230 --> 02:46.349
Yes.

02:46.350 --> 02:47.349
Your Lordship,

02:47.350 --> 02:48.509
why not forget about it?

02:48.510 --> 02:49.919
It's going to rain soon.

02:49.920 --> 02:52.290
There's a lot to prepare for the wedding.

02:52.310 --> 02:55.330
Moreover, the Fourth Young Lady said

02:55.390 --> 02:56.650
it wasn't important.

02:59.750 --> 03:00.949
I might be blindfolded,

03:00.950 --> 03:02.170
but I could hear

03:02.310 --> 03:03.530
how crucial it was

03:03.590 --> 03:05.130
when she said that.

03:06.030 --> 03:07.490
I don't want her to have any regrets.

03:19.330 --> 03:20.510
This is...

03:23.670 --> 03:25.170
This is used underneath the wine jars.

03:25.230 --> 03:26.370
Someone moved it.

03:29.330 --> 03:30.470
Lu Ming.

03:30.480 --> 03:32.650
Go and investigate
who was in charge of this garrison.

04:52.670 --> 04:56.829
=Blossom=
(Adapted from the novel "Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

04:56.830 --> 05:00.050
=Episode 19=

05:00.310 --> 05:02.210
No. Further to the right.

05:02.830 --> 05:04.309
Straighten the flower.

05:04.310 --> 05:05.450
Yes.

05:06.870 --> 05:08.410
That's more like it.

05:15.350 --> 05:17.530
There's indeed a bad person
trying to cause trouble.

05:20.070 --> 05:21.410
Both of you, come down.

05:32.550 --> 05:33.989
Does he look like a bad person?

05:33.990 --> 05:34.909
Yes.

05:34.910 --> 05:36.029
Extremely.

05:36.030 --> 05:37.570
Wait for me to count to three

05:37.750 --> 05:38.970
and let's attack together.

05:40.110 --> 05:41.250
Three!

05:46.150 --> 05:47.290
Where is he?

05:58.630 --> 06:00.250
Why did you attack me?

06:01.750 --> 06:04.090
That's what I should ask you.

06:04.110 --> 06:05.189
What are you trying to do

06:05.190 --> 06:07.229
by sneaking around the estate

06:07.230 --> 06:08.450
alone?

06:09.110 --> 06:10.370
Who are you?

06:10.630 --> 06:11.970
I am Zhao Zhangru.

06:12.100 --> 06:12.949
Dou Zhao's cousin.

06:12.950 --> 06:14.130
Who are you?

06:16.670 --> 06:17.810
Forgive me.

06:18.190 --> 06:19.770
You are from the Zhao family?

06:20.070 --> 06:21.290
In that case,

06:21.330 --> 06:22.189
please give this

06:22.190 --> 06:24.309
to the newly-wed couple, Miss Zhao.

06:24.310 --> 06:25.930
Tell them it's from Chen Jia.

06:26.510 --> 06:28.759
I wish Lord Song and his wife
a happy ever after

06:28.760 --> 06:31.370
and give birth to children soon.

06:38.430 --> 06:39.570
What a weird person.

06:43.310 --> 06:44.450
Miss Zhao.

06:44.470 --> 06:45.730
What's wrong?

06:46.430 --> 06:48.279
A bad person attacked me

06:48.280 --> 06:50.170
and gave Ms. Longevity a gift.

06:50.390 --> 06:52.149
He was weird and mysterious.

06:52.150 --> 06:53.370
A man called Chen Jia.

06:53.750 --> 06:54.890
Chen Jia?

06:54.930 --> 06:56.490
Mr. Chen was here?

06:56.810 --> 06:58.090
Shadow Guard?

06:58.100 --> 07:00.710
No wonder he was acting sneakily
even though he was giving a gift.

07:03.780 --> 07:04.909
That was weird.

07:04.910 --> 07:06.869
Why did he give
a broken jade pomegranate?

07:06.870 --> 07:09.330
Right? How weird.

07:16.230 --> 07:17.490
I broke it.

07:18.470 --> 07:23.170
(Cui's Residence)

07:24.280 --> 07:25.949
- What's going on?
- It has been so long.

07:25.950 --> 07:27.229
The auspicious hour is over.

07:27.230 --> 07:28.970
Where is the escort team?

07:29.660 --> 07:30.930
Let's wait for a while more.

07:45.590 --> 07:47.130
How is it? Is he here?

07:48.190 --> 07:50.049
We asked the men to run two li

07:50.050 --> 07:51.610
but they didn't see the escort.

07:52.670 --> 07:54.370
So unlucky?

07:54.540 --> 07:56.170
She was replaced the last time.

07:56.450 --> 07:58.330
This time,
they're breaking off the engagement.

08:02.060 --> 08:03.869
Why are you still in the mood to eat?

08:03.870 --> 08:05.210
Think of something.

08:05.750 --> 08:07.490
As long as there isn't a catastrophe,

08:07.710 --> 08:09.210
we still need to eat.

08:09.700 --> 08:11.959
Moreover, I'm sure

08:11.960 --> 08:13.970
he was held up by something.

08:19.150 --> 08:20.970
- Lord Song.
- Lord Song.

08:22.880 --> 08:23.949
- Lord Song.
- Lord Song.

08:23.950 --> 08:25.720
- This is urgent. Move.
- It's not right.

08:25.990 --> 08:27.130
Lord Song!

08:27.350 --> 08:28.229
Sorry.

08:28.230 --> 08:29.669
This is against the ritual.

08:29.670 --> 08:31.029
This won't do, Lord Song!

08:31.030 --> 08:31.909
Song Mo.

08:31.910 --> 08:32.989
You just came in like this?

08:32.990 --> 08:33.960
It's against the ritual.

08:33.970 --> 08:34.909
Lord Zhao.

08:34.910 --> 08:36.740
I have something urgent
to find Ms. Longevity.

08:36.750 --> 08:37.949
The escort will arrive soon.

08:37.950 --> 08:39.270
You missed the auspicious hour.

08:39.280 --> 08:41.060
Are you trying
to force your way through now?

08:41.630 --> 08:42.770
I'm sorry.

08:43.650 --> 08:45.410
- Lord Song!
- How can he be so rude?

08:45.710 --> 08:46.850
Stop him!

08:46.870 --> 08:48.810
You can't go inside! Come back!

08:49.590 --> 08:50.930
We'll wait for 15 more minutes.

08:51.790 --> 08:53.170
If he isn't here,

08:55.630 --> 08:56.850
I'll go and find him.

08:57.830 --> 08:59.690
You'll go and find him?

09:02.590 --> 09:03.730
Can I come in?

09:04.390 --> 09:05.429
Dou Zhao.

09:05.430 --> 09:06.570
No way.

09:06.710 --> 09:08.489
No groom
enters a bridal chamber directly.

09:08.490 --> 09:09.609
It's against the ritual.

09:09.610 --> 09:11.069
You are late for an hour.

09:11.070 --> 09:12.620
You said you'd marry Miss Dou.

09:12.630 --> 09:14.309
- Song Mo, go away!
- Why are you so rude?

09:14.310 --> 09:15.509
Dou Zhao, trust me.

09:15.510 --> 09:16.949
- Just open a gap.
- You can't go inside.

09:16.950 --> 09:17.789
I won't go inside.

09:17.790 --> 09:18.669
- I won't even take a look.
- It's inauspicious.

09:18.670 --> 09:20.069
Yantang, what are you doing?

09:20.070 --> 09:21.469
Song Mo, it's inauspicious!

09:21.470 --> 09:22.309
Dou Zhao!

09:22.310 --> 09:23.650
- Give me your hand!
- Song Mo!

09:23.790 --> 09:25.210
- Listen to me!
- Dou Zhao!

09:25.350 --> 09:26.309
Lord Song!

09:26.310 --> 09:27.709
- Dou Zhao!
- Song Mo!

09:27.710 --> 09:28.970
Get out!

09:29.630 --> 09:30.629
It's inauspicious!

09:30.630 --> 09:31.930
Yes, Lord Song!

09:32.270 --> 09:33.730
You mustn't go inside.

09:33.910 --> 09:34.749
Lord Song!

09:34.750 --> 09:36.010
- Lord Song!
- Yes, Lord Song!

09:36.670 --> 09:38.010
You mustn't enter!

09:38.670 --> 09:40.069
Why is your hand injured?

09:40.070 --> 09:41.210
It's fine.

09:41.270 --> 09:42.450
Give me your hand.

09:43.370 --> 09:45.469
How can you say you're fine
when it's so badly hurt?

09:45.470 --> 09:48.070
♪I rise on tiptoes♪

09:48.310 --> 09:50.389
♪To kiss your brow♪

09:50.390 --> 09:55.790
♪From now on,
my heart needs no disguise♪

09:56.330 --> 09:58.640
♪Wrapped in frost and snow♪

09:59.010 --> 10:01.120
♪Standing side by side with you♪

10:02.870 --> 10:04.250
How did you find it?

10:04.630 --> 10:05.669
Dong Qi!

10:05.670 --> 10:06.549
Hand over the bangle!

10:06.550 --> 10:07.589
What bangle?

10:07.590 --> 10:10.050
The jar of Nu'erhong wine
was found in your yard.

10:10.430 --> 10:11.690
Hand over the bangle.

10:12.190 --> 10:14.170
Something found in the wastelands

10:14.490 --> 10:16.690
- belongs to the person who found it.
- Give it to me!

10:17.000 --> 10:22.749
♪Not heeding the people's advice♪

10:22.750 --> 10:24.250
You want the bangle, right?

10:24.760 --> 10:26.810
I won't give it to you
even if I burn it.

10:30.220 --> 10:35.069
♪I close our distance without rest♪

10:35.070 --> 10:37.290
Since the bangle and the jar of wine
have been found,

10:37.350 --> 10:38.650
you can be at ease now.

10:39.350 --> 10:41.210
I broke the rules
by forcing my way in here.

10:41.510 --> 10:43.250
The palanquin will arrive soon.

10:43.390 --> 10:44.970
I will go out and wait for it.

10:46.400 --> 10:47.269
Wait.

10:47.270 --> 10:51.769
♪Thankfully, I have the rest of my lives
to make up for it♪

10:51.770 --> 10:56.979
♪I pick a star and hang a moon
to light up your night♪

10:56.980 --> 11:01.029
♪My heart is devoted to one person,
leaving no vacancy♪

11:01.030 --> 11:02.650
Any later and your hand will rot.

11:02.870 --> 11:05.619
I can't be at ease
to get married like this.

11:05.620 --> 11:08.110
♪Most love problems are hard to resolve♪

11:10.950 --> 11:12.210
Go back to work.

11:22.870 --> 11:24.810
Endure it. It hurts a little.

11:27.510 --> 11:30.250
A perfect couple, as flawless as jade.

11:30.750 --> 11:33.610
Their love is as sincere
and pure as the jade.

11:34.350 --> 11:37.629
I can see that Yantang is sincere.

11:37.630 --> 11:39.370
The grudge from the last generation

11:39.750 --> 11:41.490
is all over.

11:41.830 --> 11:45.050
Let's hope they can live well together

11:45.590 --> 11:47.050
in this life.

11:53.030 --> 11:56.970
(Double Happiness)

12:01.150 --> 12:02.370
Hurry up!

12:04.190 --> 12:06.429
The groom has many betrothal gifts!

12:06.430 --> 12:07.690
Move them all inside!

12:08.390 --> 12:09.530
Hurry up!

12:09.950 --> 12:11.570
Don't miss the auspicious hour!

12:16.710 --> 12:20.130
Dou Zhao, 4th daughter of
North Tower's 6th generation Dou family

12:20.630 --> 12:23.130
will be married to the Song family.

12:23.470 --> 12:25.469
I'm filled with emotions.

12:25.470 --> 12:28.090
(Dou Zhao's Mother,
Zhao's Memorial Tablet)

12:33.590 --> 12:35.370
I'm ordered by my father

12:35.490 --> 12:36.850
to celebrate this joyous occasion.

12:36.910 --> 12:38.130
I'm awaiting your orders.

12:38.470 --> 12:40.130
After marrying into his family,

12:40.190 --> 12:42.349
you must obey him.

12:42.350 --> 12:44.370
You must think of him all the time

12:44.750 --> 12:46.570
and not go against this.

12:58.350 --> 13:01.930
This is my savings for all these years.

13:02.950 --> 13:04.090
Don't worry.

13:04.190 --> 13:06.290
I also prepared for Ming.

13:07.710 --> 13:08.890
I know

13:09.270 --> 13:11.829
you've been aggrieved
for all these years, Ms. Longevity.

13:11.830 --> 13:13.890
I sold a few of my shops

13:14.150 --> 13:15.490
for your dowry.

13:16.350 --> 13:17.490
Father.

13:20.030 --> 13:21.330
Song Yantang,

13:21.950 --> 13:23.530
if you treat her well,

13:24.130 --> 13:27.610
The Dou and Cui family
will be on your side.

13:28.060 --> 13:29.829
If you treat her badly,

13:29.830 --> 13:31.709
we won't forgive you.

13:31.710 --> 13:33.589
I will remember it

13:33.590 --> 13:34.970
and do what I promised.

13:40.870 --> 13:43.890
Previously, her stepmother troubled her
and her uncle suppressed her.

13:44.350 --> 13:45.470
Right now, it seems like

13:45.480 --> 13:48.060
there's still someone in the Dou family
who loves this daughter.

13:48.350 --> 13:51.050
♪The glitter of the beautiful terrace
is just a fleeting splendour♪

13:51.270 --> 13:53.570
(Twilight in Spring)

13:55.000 --> 13:56.449
♪Bending down for a single kiss♪

13:56.450 --> 14:00.850
♪Forsaking words of farewell♪

14:01.500 --> 14:04.160
♪The golden fiery steed
rides across the vast horizon♪

14:04.770 --> 14:07.910
♪In this life, oh♪

14:08.040 --> 14:13.340
♪Without you, what is there to envy?♪

14:13.807 --> 14:16.219
♪Let me lay down my blade
and leave the sea of battles♪

14:16.220 --> 14:20.579
♪To adorn your hair with a jade hairpin♪

14:20.580 --> 14:27.280
♪Let a thousand, ten thousand blossoms♪

14:28.460 --> 14:30.210
Give it to me!

14:30.950 --> 14:33.780
♪With bold strokes and vibrant colors♪

14:34.030 --> 14:35.770
♪And for all else♪

14:35.870 --> 14:42.420
♪Let it remain pale and void♪

14:45.870 --> 14:47.190
Congratulations.

14:59.790 --> 15:01.069
Such extravagance.

15:01.070 --> 15:02.610
Dou Zhao must be so happy.

15:02.990 --> 15:05.269
Dou Shiying gave her

15:05.270 --> 15:06.450
all her assets.

15:06.990 --> 15:08.690
How can Ming

15:08.790 --> 15:11.930
face her in-laws
with such unfair treatment?

15:20.630 --> 15:22.110
Have you sent the letter?

15:22.130 --> 15:23.880
It has been sent to
Duke of Ying's Residence

15:23.890 --> 15:25.610
according to your orders.

15:26.950 --> 15:29.770
That place seems to be filled
with glory and splendor,

15:30.230 --> 15:33.090
but it is a dangerous den.

15:33.170 --> 15:35.530
Both the father and son
are involved in battles.

15:36.010 --> 15:38.370
There won't be peace in the future.

15:38.910 --> 15:41.650
Her father-in-law is more cruel than me.

15:41.870 --> 15:45.090
I want to see how she gets married.

15:45.847 --> 15:49.189
Zhao has lived in a manor since young

15:49.190 --> 15:50.810
and lacked education.

15:51.180 --> 15:52.570
She knows nothing about customs.

15:53.150 --> 15:55.690
Zhao seems obedient

15:55.890 --> 15:58.290
but she is reckless.

15:58.520 --> 16:01.010
Duke, please forgive her

16:01.170 --> 16:03.850
and educate her in the future.

16:07.030 --> 16:10.109
(Wang Yingxue)
Wang Yingxue's letter seems sincere

16:10.110 --> 16:11.749
but the true meaning

16:11.750 --> 16:14.469
is that Dou Zhao is a vulgar woman

16:14.470 --> 16:17.050
who is kind of the surface
but a wolf at heart.

16:17.170 --> 16:19.709
Her stepmother is not the only one
who is dissatisfied with her.

16:19.710 --> 16:22.210
I purposely went and asked around.

16:22.470 --> 16:24.149
Even the children on the streets

16:24.150 --> 16:25.949
said the Fourth Young Lady
of the Dou family

16:25.950 --> 16:28.890
would even take their kites.

16:28.990 --> 16:30.149
She's so fierce.

16:30.150 --> 16:33.210
Dou Zhao is obviously a vixen.

16:33.990 --> 16:38.490
Lord Song might suffer from now on.

16:40.350 --> 16:42.610
I'm very happy for my son

16:43.510 --> 16:45.770
to be marrying such a strong woman.

16:47.790 --> 16:48.709
I can't wait.

16:48.710 --> 16:50.490
Let's go and welcome the bride.

16:53.430 --> 16:55.269
(Double Happiness)

16:55.270 --> 16:56.690
The auspicious hour is here.

16:56.870 --> 16:58.290
Carry out the ritual.

17:12.310 --> 17:15.370
(Virtuous Wife,
Madam Jiang's Memorial Tablet)

17:18.230 --> 17:20.090
Bow to the parents.

17:27.710 --> 17:31.290
His Highness and
Grand Princess Shude is here!

17:38.950 --> 17:41.370
Your Highness.

17:41.390 --> 17:43.730
Forgive me for not welcoming you.

17:44.070 --> 17:47.090
I came here to congratulate you
on His Majesty's decree.

17:48.270 --> 17:51.090
Greetings, Grand Princess.
Greetings, Your Highness.

17:51.790 --> 17:53.490
Duke of Ying, heed the decree.

17:57.190 --> 18:00.050
By Heaven's mandate,
the emperor's edict is as follows.

18:00.310 --> 18:02.989
Duke of Ying's eldest son
and Dou family's fourth daughter

18:02.990 --> 18:04.610
are married.

18:04.647 --> 18:06.549
I am very happy.

18:06.550 --> 18:11.010
I'm giving a Sheng and a bell
to Song and Dou respectively.

18:11.230 --> 18:12.869
I hope both families

18:12.870 --> 18:14.589
can live harmoniously

18:14.590 --> 18:16.570
and love each other for a long time.

18:16.750 --> 18:18.330
That is all.

18:19.110 --> 18:21.570
I accept the edict.

18:31.970 --> 18:34.850
I heard Duke of Ying
is good at playing the Sheng.

18:34.910 --> 18:36.410
I'm sure you know

18:36.650 --> 18:38.410
that no matter
how well the Sheng sounds,

18:38.430 --> 18:41.370
it still won't be better than
when it is played with the bell.

18:42.590 --> 18:45.621
A good father and a filial son
live in harmony

18:45.622 --> 18:46.749
is the only way

18:46.750 --> 18:50.530
to not disappoint your family's honor
for five generations.

18:50.930 --> 18:54.690
I will remember His Majesty's teaching.

18:56.870 --> 18:58.410
The ritual continues!

18:58.550 --> 19:00.530
Step over the brazier!

19:02.150 --> 19:05.610
(Loyalty and Devotion in Love)

19:15.670 --> 19:17.970
Enter the bridal chamber!

19:19.830 --> 19:21.570
Why isn't Su here yet?

19:22.870 --> 19:24.010
Hurry!

19:26.310 --> 19:27.450
This is rare.

19:27.460 --> 19:29.010
Leading a donkey on Changle Street?

19:29.110 --> 19:31.850
Yizhi Hall has no donkey shed for you.

19:34.070 --> 19:35.349
Today is His Lordship's wedding.

19:35.350 --> 19:36.970
No one can enter.

19:37.470 --> 19:38.879
I am the bride's good friend.

19:38.880 --> 19:40.090
I'm here to attend the banquet.

19:40.400 --> 19:41.659
However, merchants

19:41.660 --> 19:43.980
cannot wear silk
and ride a horse carriage.

19:44.520 --> 19:45.690
Do you have an invitation?

19:46.110 --> 19:47.870
I have too many goods.

19:47.880 --> 19:50.039
When I find the invitation,
I might miss the banquet.

19:50.040 --> 19:52.579
A merchant lady is a good friend
of His Lordship's wife?

19:52.580 --> 19:55.170
I am the childhood friend
of the Jade Emperor.

19:56.910 --> 19:58.490
You're looking down on others.

19:59.230 --> 20:00.370
Second Young Master.

20:02.200 --> 20:03.610
What's wrong with being a merchant?

20:03.630 --> 20:05.570
She makes money with her own wisdom.

20:05.830 --> 20:08.170
She's a lot better than
the flunkies of big families.

20:11.240 --> 20:12.380
I am Song Han.

20:12.480 --> 20:15.460
I've heard my sister-in-law was close
to the daughter of the great merchants

20:15.470 --> 20:16.330
of the Miao family.

20:17.030 --> 20:18.170
You must be

20:18.470 --> 20:20.010
Young Lady Miao.

20:20.590 --> 20:21.970
Thank you, Second Young Master.

20:22.110 --> 20:24.189
These are all Zhao's personal assets.

20:24.190 --> 20:25.850
I don't know how I should...

20:26.670 --> 20:27.810
Here you go.

20:30.390 --> 20:31.570
Your face.

20:36.310 --> 20:38.709
Someone, move the boxes
to the inner courtyard.

20:38.710 --> 20:39.850
Yes.

20:40.190 --> 20:41.330
Hurry.

20:42.190 --> 20:43.450
Thank you, Young Lady.

20:43.670 --> 20:46.570
I'll ask someone to bring you
to the inner hall to wash up.

20:46.605 --> 20:47.549
Don't worry.

20:47.550 --> 20:49.530
I won't let you
miss the cross-cupped wine ritual.

20:49.710 --> 20:50.890
Thank you, Young Master.

20:52.550 --> 20:58.419
Lift the veil!

20:58.420 --> 21:01.010
Lift the veil!

21:06.470 --> 21:09.970
Great!

21:10.390 --> 21:13.229
The groom must sit on the veil.

21:13.230 --> 21:15.669
In the future, you will
always suppress the bride.

21:15.670 --> 21:17.730
The wife follows the husband.

21:18.710 --> 21:20.210
My residence has no such rule.

21:20.390 --> 21:22.090
My wife and I are equal.

21:22.350 --> 21:23.669
Please skip

21:23.670 --> 21:25.130
every ritual of this kind.

21:25.550 --> 21:26.690
That's...

21:27.470 --> 21:28.909
Respecting and loving each other

21:28.910 --> 21:30.690
is the way a relationship can last long.

21:31.379 --> 21:32.549
Right!

21:32.550 --> 21:34.330
Serve the cross-cupped wine.

21:34.710 --> 21:36.690
Seems like someone
who cares not about rules.

21:38.350 --> 21:41.149
Yantang is suppressed by her.

21:41.150 --> 21:43.650
No one knows what the residence
will become in the future.

21:51.350 --> 21:54.970
The newlyweds hold the cup
and drink with respect to each other.

21:55.030 --> 21:59.410
From now on, husband and wife are one
and share weal and woe.

22:01.950 --> 22:03.949
Tying each other's hair into a knot.

22:03.950 --> 22:06.350
Informing each other
of the intention to grow old together.

22:18.670 --> 22:20.469
Great!

22:20.470 --> 22:21.789
From now on,

22:21.790 --> 22:24.069
both of you will live in harmony

22:24.070 --> 22:25.770
until you grow old.

22:26.870 --> 22:28.709
The ritual is completed!

22:28.710 --> 22:30.389
- Great!
- Great!

22:30.390 --> 22:31.239
Let's go and drink!

22:31.240 --> 22:32.309
- Lord Song, let's go and drink.
- Let's go.

22:32.310 --> 22:33.149
- Let's go.
- Let's drink.

22:33.150 --> 22:34.630
Yantang.

22:34.760 --> 22:36.010
My wife has something to say.

22:36.650 --> 22:37.829
- Quick!
- Come back early.

22:37.830 --> 22:39.330
I have something to give you.

22:39.350 --> 22:40.389
- All right. I'll come back soon.
- Talk after you come back.

22:40.390 --> 22:41.509
Let's go and drink.

22:41.510 --> 22:42.549
Let's go.

22:42.550 --> 22:43.690
Let's drink.

22:46.280 --> 22:48.189
We won't let you come back
unless you're drunk.

22:48.190 --> 22:49.330
Quick!

22:50.590 --> 22:52.610
Yantang has changed.

22:53.010 --> 22:54.909
Madam Jiang used to say

22:54.910 --> 22:56.839
this child was careless.

22:56.840 --> 22:58.389
He would either wear the wrong clothes

22:58.390 --> 23:00.210
or wear unmatched shoes or socks.

23:01.150 --> 23:02.709
Today, he has finally met

23:02.710 --> 23:04.890
the person he loves.

23:06.350 --> 23:08.269
The ritual can progress smoothly

23:08.270 --> 23:09.770
thanks to you, Grand Princess.

23:10.310 --> 23:11.770
Take a seat.

23:12.270 --> 23:13.709
Think of me as shamelessly asking you

23:13.710 --> 23:15.410
to bless me by pressing the bed.

23:15.550 --> 23:16.690
Come here.

23:17.190 --> 23:18.330
Sit down.

23:20.350 --> 23:22.949
This ritual requires a blessed person
who has a good marriage

23:22.950 --> 23:25.610
with a son and a daughter.

23:25.950 --> 23:27.189
I have no son and no daughter

23:27.190 --> 23:29.730
and have lived alone
for more than a decade.

23:30.910 --> 23:32.170
I think

23:32.430 --> 23:35.370
someone who can live freely
and be at ease

23:35.710 --> 23:37.090
is a blessed person.

23:39.110 --> 23:40.669
I finally know

23:40.670 --> 23:43.010
why Yantang loves you so much.

23:46.718 --> 23:47.898
What did you say?

23:48.590 --> 23:51.389
The Duke welcomed Dou Zhao

23:51.390 --> 23:53.130
into his family happily?

23:53.390 --> 23:55.189
I said it clearly in my letter.

23:55.190 --> 23:57.709
Dou Zhao is a rude brat

23:57.710 --> 23:59.490
who cannot be educated.

23:59.550 --> 24:00.469
Perhaps the Duke

24:00.470 --> 24:01.970
was dull

24:02.070 --> 24:04.029
and couldn't understand you.

24:04.030 --> 24:06.290
Is it my fault
for not writing the letter clearly?

24:08.950 --> 24:10.850
It seems like the Duke

24:10.910 --> 24:13.210
is a foolish father who lacks sense.

24:13.470 --> 24:16.130
No wonder he couldn't
win against his son.

24:16.310 --> 24:19.210
(Yizhi Hall)

24:21.630 --> 24:23.389
I couldn't trust Lord Song previously.

24:23.390 --> 24:24.589
But it seems like

24:24.590 --> 24:26.269
he is really nice to Zhao.

24:26.270 --> 24:27.469
I feel happy for Zhao.

24:27.470 --> 24:29.010
Me too.

24:29.150 --> 24:31.549
However, I envy her as well.

24:31.550 --> 24:34.250
It's not easy to find a good man.

24:34.710 --> 24:36.989
When can I finally find one,

24:36.990 --> 24:38.130
Su?

24:41.830 --> 24:43.270
You are siblings,

24:43.280 --> 24:45.250
but your accuracy
in Chinese Checkers is so bad.

24:45.390 --> 24:47.210
You've lost three games consecutively.

24:51.070 --> 24:53.309
It's embarrassing
to wear this jade belt.

24:53.310 --> 24:55.690
Why not give it to me instead
as a prize?

24:56.750 --> 24:57.949
It's just his bad luck.

24:57.950 --> 24:59.830
I can help Second Young Master
win against you.

25:00.770 --> 25:02.869
Second Young Master,
you are bad at Chinese Checkers

25:02.870 --> 25:04.349
but your luck with women is good.

25:04.350 --> 25:07.050
Even a merchant is trying to help you.

25:08.950 --> 25:10.230
His Majesty gave me this belt.

25:10.240 --> 25:12.029
Young Master Mu,
if you want it as a prize,

25:12.030 --> 25:13.360
are you disrespecting His Majesty?

25:13.370 --> 25:14.930
So what?

25:15.410 --> 25:17.109
Second Young Master
is good at swordplay.

25:17.110 --> 25:19.330
Why don't we do swordplay
while reciting poems?

25:19.382 --> 25:20.962
The last time I see you do that,

25:20.990 --> 25:22.810
"Wearing the stone orchid
and the Duheng herb,

25:22.820 --> 25:25.030
plucking a fresh flower
to express my longing for you."

25:25.040 --> 25:27.090
The swordplay for that poem was good.

25:27.350 --> 25:29.749
I despise people
who talk about your background.

25:29.750 --> 25:31.750
You act arrogant
and think you're high and mighty.

25:31.870 --> 25:33.010
That's right!

25:34.030 --> 25:35.570
What does the poem mean?

25:36.890 --> 25:38.989
- Stop talking.
- She doesn't know "Mountain Spirit"?

25:38.990 --> 25:41.770
The Lord's wife has a friend like that?

25:42.910 --> 25:44.109
I know the Mountain Spirit!

25:44.110 --> 25:45.029
I know Qu Yuan as well!

25:45.030 --> 25:46.540
I don't know it when they are combined!

25:46.550 --> 25:47.680
I don't know it, so what?

25:47.690 --> 25:49.960
Isn't it good enough
that the rice dumplings are delicious

25:49.970 --> 25:50.709
and the wine is good?

25:50.710 --> 25:52.349
You want to play
Chinese Checkers, right?

25:52.350 --> 25:53.490
Fine.

25:54.470 --> 25:56.170
Let me play with you.

25:56.350 --> 25:58.650
Dou Zhao grows up in a manor.

25:59.030 --> 26:01.650
Is she as rude as you?

26:03.750 --> 26:04.589
I...

26:04.590 --> 26:05.770
(Find the Truth)

26:06.210 --> 26:07.749
My Lordship, be careful of the stairs.

26:07.750 --> 26:08.890
Song Mo.

26:08.910 --> 26:10.770
Song Mo, don't go.

26:10.870 --> 26:13.610
I can't drink.

26:13.630 --> 26:14.829
Yes, Your Highness.

26:14.830 --> 26:17.130
How can the Young General

26:17.710 --> 26:21.290
lose when it comes to drinking?

26:21.750 --> 26:22.860
Keep drinking!

26:22.870 --> 26:24.269
- Your Highness.
- Your Highness.

26:24.270 --> 26:25.320
Look at Song Mo.

26:25.330 --> 26:27.500
- Your Highness.
- He will vomit if he keeps drinking.

26:27.510 --> 26:28.650
My wife.

26:29.830 --> 26:31.989
Dou Zhao is waiting for you.

26:31.990 --> 26:33.370
I understand.

26:33.830 --> 26:35.709
Go back.

26:35.710 --> 26:37.989
- Be careful, Your Highness.
- Thank you, Your Highness.

26:37.990 --> 26:40.090
- Let's keep drinking.
- Enjoy, Your Highness!

26:40.250 --> 26:41.149
- Let's go.
- Come on.

26:41.150 --> 26:42.290
This way.

26:42.750 --> 26:43.890
Let's drink!

26:52.830 --> 26:55.610
You are only
thinking about Dou Zhao now.

26:55.670 --> 26:56.669
A buddy who is married

26:56.670 --> 26:58.250
is no longer loyal.

26:58.830 --> 27:00.269
You are busy training the troops

27:00.270 --> 27:01.690
and are married.

27:01.870 --> 27:03.429
I don't think there's a chance

27:03.430 --> 27:05.610
to drink like this anymore
in the future.

27:05.670 --> 27:06.810
You told me yourself.

27:07.350 --> 27:09.810
A woman will have a huge grudge
if you make her wait.

27:12.430 --> 27:14.890
Do you not care about
your buddy's grudge then?

27:15.150 --> 27:16.450
You just value her more than us.

27:18.270 --> 27:20.650
Congratulations on your marriage,
Your Lordship.

27:21.390 --> 27:22.530
Thank you, Your Lordship.

27:22.670 --> 27:23.709
Thank you, Your Lordship.

27:23.710 --> 27:24.850
You may leave.

27:41.710 --> 27:42.850
Ms. Longevity.

27:44.190 --> 27:45.330
Ms. Longevity.

27:45.870 --> 27:47.010
Come here.

27:49.750 --> 27:51.010
Why are you here?

27:51.720 --> 27:52.860
Shush.

27:53.030 --> 27:54.170
Come here.

27:55.510 --> 27:56.650
Your Highness.

27:56.670 --> 27:58.989
We've searched all over Yizhi Hall.

27:58.990 --> 28:00.370
We didn't find the letter.

28:02.550 --> 28:03.970
- Yes!
- Yes!

28:12.560 --> 28:15.909
A few days ago, hidden scouts discovered the
messenger who sent the letter to Uncle

28:15.910 --> 28:17.370
was brought to Eastern Palace indeed.

28:17.710 --> 28:18.890
His fate is unknown

28:19.190 --> 28:21.410
and the letter is missing.

28:22.730 --> 28:24.230
Are you suspecting His Highness?

28:26.158 --> 28:27.469
He has been suspicious of me

28:27.470 --> 28:28.629
and kept testing me.

28:28.630 --> 28:30.330
He must have a secret.

28:30.670 --> 28:33.450
We still don't know whether people inside
or outside the residence

28:33.550 --> 28:34.810
is friend or foe.

28:36.950 --> 28:38.570
It's so dangerous.

28:39.590 --> 28:41.490
Aren't you afraid that I might run away?

28:44.790 --> 28:46.090
I was just joking.

28:53.710 --> 28:56.610
You amaze me, dear.

29:00.030 --> 29:01.890
Let me remove your crown for you.

29:15.110 --> 29:16.410
You are so pretty, my dear.

29:18.190 --> 29:19.330
Come with me.

29:25.630 --> 29:26.770
Sit down.

29:29.110 --> 29:30.890
I have something to give you.

29:31.310 --> 29:33.090
I hid it for many years.

29:33.470 --> 29:35.050
I'm sure you want to see it as well.

29:35.710 --> 29:36.850
Wait for me.

30:15.750 --> 30:16.890
Don't peek.

30:36.790 --> 30:39.890
I obtained a storybook
called Records of the Enlightened Age.

30:40.570 --> 30:44.050
This is the chart
that is recorded inside.

30:44.950 --> 30:47.770
The story matches
the current situation.

30:48.490 --> 30:49.890
In Records of the Enlightened Age,

30:49.900 --> 30:52.590
Lord Qing will commit treason
in the 27th year of the Chengping era

30:52.610 --> 30:54.090
which is next year.

31:04.710 --> 31:05.890
As expected of

31:06.510 --> 31:09.410
the female Zhuge Liang I married
after visiting Zhending three times.

31:10.190 --> 31:12.149
Did I not make myself clear?

31:12.150 --> 31:13.690
This is treason.

31:13.710 --> 31:16.370
Why do you look so indifferent?

31:17.070 --> 31:18.430
It's not that I feel indifferent.

31:18.510 --> 31:21.650
His Majesty only has two sons.

31:21.950 --> 31:23.709
Who ascends the throne

31:23.710 --> 31:25.010
is still undecided.

31:25.110 --> 31:27.890
Even if Lord Qing
is going to rule the land,

31:28.070 --> 31:29.210
it's also

31:30.750 --> 31:32.890
not surprising, right?

31:35.590 --> 31:36.730
You are right.

31:37.770 --> 31:39.069
However, the issue

31:39.070 --> 31:40.779
is not with Lord Qing
or the crown prince

31:40.780 --> 31:42.170
but you.

31:42.300 --> 31:44.759
You have control
of the Imperial Guard now.

31:44.760 --> 31:46.970
No one can go against you.

31:47.070 --> 31:48.349
What they need to do now

31:48.350 --> 31:49.949
is to get your support

31:49.950 --> 31:51.250
or overturn you.

31:56.230 --> 31:59.210
Thank you
for telling me everything honestly.

32:00.350 --> 32:02.690
However, there's no rush about this.

32:03.110 --> 32:04.250
Today

32:05.470 --> 32:07.130
is our wedding.

32:11.150 --> 32:12.349
Yes.

32:12.350 --> 32:13.549
It's all my fault.

32:13.550 --> 32:15.589
I always want to tell you

32:15.590 --> 32:17.210
everything on my mind.

32:17.710 --> 32:19.890
I didn't take note of the time.

32:20.190 --> 32:22.290
There's no rush indeed.

32:49.270 --> 32:50.690
You haven't eaten the whole day.

32:50.750 --> 32:52.010
I'm sure you are starving.

32:52.030 --> 32:54.010
Let me order the kitchen
to make you some food.

32:54.270 --> 32:55.690
There's no need.

32:55.830 --> 32:57.989
I don't want the servants to think

32:57.990 --> 33:01.010
you've married a wife who is a glutton.

33:02.950 --> 33:03.989
Sure.

33:03.990 --> 33:05.130
I'll cook for you.

33:08.110 --> 33:09.229
Let me grill it.

33:09.230 --> 33:10.730
Your hand is injured.

33:11.590 --> 33:12.730
It's all right.

33:12.790 --> 33:13.930
Let me do it.

33:18.590 --> 33:19.730
A year ago,

33:20.230 --> 33:22.810
you were threatening me
with a sword on my neck.

33:23.590 --> 33:25.050
I didn't expect us

33:25.230 --> 33:26.890
to become a family a year later.

33:29.950 --> 33:31.210
A family.

33:32.590 --> 33:35.010
I grew up with my uncle
in the military camp.

33:35.350 --> 33:37.250
I don't know
how it feels to be with a family.

33:38.230 --> 33:40.850
Until I see Uncle and Aunt together,

33:41.110 --> 33:42.330
I finally understood

33:43.070 --> 33:45.090
that a family should look like them.

33:45.670 --> 33:47.050
What about the Duke's Residence?

33:50.150 --> 33:53.210
I mean when Madam Jiang was still alive.

33:54.550 --> 33:55.690
Back then,

33:57.790 --> 33:58.930
I also didn't have a family.

34:02.830 --> 34:03.970
Me too.

34:04.990 --> 34:08.690
When I was young, I saw other people
having three members in their families.

34:09.830 --> 34:11.050
I was wondering

34:11.830 --> 34:14.650
why Mother would abandon me

34:15.390 --> 34:18.010
and why I couldn't stop it.

34:20.070 --> 34:21.570
When I couldn't figure it out,

34:21.950 --> 34:23.650
I would hide in the hills.

34:24.710 --> 34:27.389
I saw Gao Laozhuang's chubby wife

34:27.390 --> 34:29.890
chasing after him after he got drunk.

34:30.110 --> 34:32.610
Everyone from the estate
would come out and watch.

34:33.350 --> 34:34.789
I also saw

34:34.790 --> 34:38.389
how a mover would buy
two biscuits for his daughter

34:38.390 --> 34:40.970
after he walked the streets.

34:42.190 --> 34:44.410
After meeting many people
and experiencing many things,

34:44.550 --> 34:45.810
I realised

34:46.270 --> 34:47.890
there were

34:47.910 --> 34:49.610
many kinds of families.

34:50.350 --> 34:54.010
However, there are more good families
than the bad ones.

34:57.750 --> 35:01.090
There are benefits
of growing up in the military camp too.

35:01.550 --> 35:03.090
I learned how to be independent.

35:03.870 --> 35:05.869
I'm best at making grilled fish.

35:05.870 --> 35:07.090
It's my own recipe.

35:07.570 --> 35:08.710
Try it.

35:19.790 --> 35:20.909
I heard

35:20.910 --> 35:24.050
you could slice a living fish
3,000 times

35:24.350 --> 35:27.050
and it could still swim
after releasing it back into the water.

35:27.350 --> 35:28.570
Is it true?

35:30.510 --> 35:31.650
It's too late

35:31.910 --> 35:33.050
to feel afraid now.

35:48.870 --> 35:50.800
Ms. Longevity!

35:53.910 --> 35:55.050
Zhangru.

35:55.110 --> 35:57.690
Both of you are really here.

35:58.150 --> 35:59.930
Don't cry.

36:00.350 --> 36:01.810
Don't cry, Zhangru.

36:02.030 --> 36:03.290
Don't cry.

36:03.870 --> 36:05.290
All right.

36:06.070 --> 36:07.570
Who bullied you?

36:08.030 --> 36:09.749
Who could bully me?

36:09.750 --> 36:11.210
I'm happy.

36:11.510 --> 36:12.650
Ms. Longevity,

36:12.950 --> 36:14.349
I'm 99% happy

36:14.350 --> 36:16.530
that you're married today.

36:16.830 --> 36:20.290
However, there's a little sadness.

36:20.390 --> 36:22.349
It's hard to find a good man

36:22.350 --> 36:23.530
to marry happily.

36:23.590 --> 36:24.469
However, I think

36:24.470 --> 36:26.749
I will never get married in my life.

36:26.750 --> 36:29.149
There are many men in this world.

36:29.150 --> 36:30.269
It's not difficult

36:30.270 --> 36:31.610
to find a good one.

36:32.910 --> 36:34.050
Your Lordship,

36:34.390 --> 36:35.930
am I right?

36:38.350 --> 36:40.170
Yes. Of course.

36:42.030 --> 36:44.590
They are all capable soldiers
of the Imperial Guard.

36:44.600 --> 36:47.749
They have a clean background, a military
position, and achievements in battle.

36:47.750 --> 36:49.810
Most of them have
even been granted a title.

36:53.710 --> 36:54.850
They won't do.

36:54.950 --> 36:57.930
Those who are physically capable
are simple-minded.

37:00.750 --> 37:01.869
Zhangru.

37:01.870 --> 37:03.269
Just tell us

37:03.270 --> 37:04.810
your requirements honestly.

37:05.510 --> 37:07.029
Let His Lordship help you search.

37:07.030 --> 37:10.050
There were also scholars
among the Imperial Guards.

37:10.390 --> 37:11.530
Scholars?

37:11.790 --> 37:12.749
No way.

37:12.750 --> 37:14.240
They are always talking pedantically.

37:14.250 --> 37:15.610
So annoying.

37:16.790 --> 37:18.530
The person I like

37:19.150 --> 37:20.930
must have a skill

37:21.230 --> 37:22.810
and knows a bit of martial arts,

37:22.990 --> 37:24.330
so he can protect me.

37:28.350 --> 37:30.210
He needs to be handsome

37:32.510 --> 37:34.170
and cool.

37:35.510 --> 37:37.210
Most importantly,

37:37.790 --> 37:39.490
he should be quite polite.

37:39.830 --> 37:40.970
Forgive me.

37:41.190 --> 37:42.810
You are from the Zhao family?

37:44.830 --> 37:45.970
Zhangru.

37:46.510 --> 37:48.330
Do you already have a candidate

37:48.350 --> 37:50.410
for the person you like?

37:52.230 --> 37:53.690
- I...
- Who is it?

37:54.990 --> 37:55.869
Who is it?

37:55.870 --> 37:56.709
No.

37:56.710 --> 37:58.050
I was simply saying.

38:00.350 --> 38:02.130
It's not even close.

38:25.630 --> 38:26.770
Ms. Longevity.

38:26.870 --> 38:29.730
I broke your gift
that blesses you with more children.

38:29.750 --> 38:32.469
Don't worry. I fixed it for you.

38:32.470 --> 38:35.290
Otherwise, you won't get many children.

38:35.870 --> 38:37.730
(What is she talking about
in her sleep?)

39:23.470 --> 39:24.690
Good morning, Your Lordship.

39:26.190 --> 39:27.039
Your Lordship,

39:27.040 --> 39:28.810
why did you come out from your study?

39:33.310 --> 39:34.970
(Find the Truth)

39:35.350 --> 39:36.490
Your Lordship.

39:45.510 --> 39:46.810
Are you awake, Ms. Longevity?

39:58.270 --> 39:59.450
Have you seen Ms. Longevity?

39:59.670 --> 40:00.519
I haven't.

40:00.520 --> 40:01.670
What's wrong?

40:02.030 --> 40:03.930
The bride ran away last night?

40:07.870 --> 40:09.010
Your Lordship.

40:09.710 --> 40:11.330
Mr. Chen, where's my wife?

40:11.790 --> 40:12.930
Come with me.

40:18.470 --> 40:19.610
Your Lordship.

40:31.290 --> 40:33.169
(Virtuous Wife,
Madam Jiang's Memorial Tablet)

40:33.170 --> 40:34.310
Madam Jiang,

40:35.110 --> 40:38.250
Dou Zhao should address you
as my mother-in-law today.

40:39.590 --> 40:41.610
I'm sure you are surprised as well.

40:42.470 --> 40:45.250
I actually married Yantang.

40:46.730 --> 40:49.930
He was domineering at first.

40:50.470 --> 40:52.810
I was afraid of him and avoided him.

40:53.790 --> 40:55.010
Gradually,

40:55.870 --> 40:57.570
I knew about the pain in his heart.

40:58.630 --> 41:01.370
The death of the Duke of Ding
almost killed him.

41:01.870 --> 41:03.170
Later, you passed away

41:03.590 --> 41:05.410
and his father wanted to harm him.

41:06.030 --> 41:08.309
Loyalty and filial piety
became blades that hurt him.

41:08.310 --> 41:09.429
(Achievements Like Mountain)

41:09.430 --> 41:11.930
Who wouldn't go mad
after experiencing all that?

41:13.590 --> 41:16.650
Thankfully, he has endured everything.

41:18.150 --> 41:20.010
I will always be by his side

41:21.430 --> 41:23.370
and not let him repeat his mistakes.

41:24.590 --> 41:26.050
In the future,

41:26.270 --> 41:28.730
I will support Yantang

41:29.170 --> 41:30.730
and help him fulfill his wish.

41:56.670 --> 41:59.469
(Virtuous Wife,
Madam Jiang's Memorial Tablet)

41:59.470 --> 42:00.610
Mother,

42:01.910 --> 42:03.130
you may rest in peace.

42:03.950 --> 42:05.170
I am no longer alone

42:06.470 --> 42:08.050
in the future.

42:14.390 --> 42:15.530
(Mother,)

42:15.790 --> 42:18.050
(she is the one
I must protect all my life.)

42:18.750 --> 42:20.770
(If you are protecting me from Heaven,)

42:21.990 --> 42:23.210
(I beg you)

42:24.750 --> 42:26.530
(to protect her as well.)

42:43.190 --> 42:44.330
Yantang.

42:45.510 --> 42:46.349
Call me Husband.

42:46.350 --> 42:47.510
Song Mo.

42:47.770 --> 42:51.110
♪Like the moon hiding in the ocean♪

42:52.310 --> 42:54.309
I've given you so much money
over all these years

42:54.310 --> 42:55.589
but you're calling me annoying?

42:55.590 --> 42:56.429
Heaven is blind.

42:56.430 --> 43:00.010
Someone who keeps asking for money
should be struck by lightning!

43:00.750 --> 43:04.469
♪Like the sun
waiting for the flying wild geese♪

43:04.470 --> 43:07.860
♪The sound of weapons
chasing the long whip♪

43:08.350 --> 43:14.430
♪Never tired after a hundred battles,
because of you♪

43:14.740 --> 43:16.649
♪Morning and night, we meet again♪

43:16.650 --> 43:18.209
♪Walking slowly towards the distance♪

43:18.210 --> 43:21.580
♪Like leaves tangled in the wind,
tightly intertwined♪

43:21.620 --> 43:23.719
♪Together with you, wing to wing♪

43:23.720 --> 43:28.449
♪Our shadows flying,
dwelling together year after year♪

43:28.450 --> 43:30.229
♪Morning and night, with clear skies♪

43:30.230 --> 43:32.410
♪Clear wind and bright moon,
we wait for them♪

43:32.610 --> 43:35.229
♪Waiting for the fog to disperse
and the clouds to clear♪

43:35.230 --> 43:37.069
♪Tears that fall,
half a lifetime of tears♪

43:37.070 --> 43:41.470
♪Melted by your kiss,
melted by your kiss♪

43:42.010 --> 43:44.199
♪In this life, I wish to be
like Mandarin ducks in the water♪

43:44.200 --> 43:46.170
♪The green shore
is more beautiful than the sky♪

43:46.350 --> 43:48.999
♪The splendor
doesn't intoxicate the eyes♪

43:49.000 --> 43:50.729
♪Spring returns,
the swaying green lotus♪

43:50.730 --> 43:53.240
♪The mountains are distant,
what do I have to envy?♪

43:53.241 --> 43:55.749
♪Even so, I don't envy them♪

43:55.750 --> 43:57.959
♪In this life,
I wish to keep my promise to you♪

43:57.960 --> 44:00.139
♪Unchanged even to old age♪

44:00.140 --> 44:02.749
♪I will definitely
fulfill the promise without fail♪

44:02.750 --> 44:08.840
♪Seeing the full moon
even at the end of the world♪

44:17.110 --> 44:19.259
♪In this life, I wish to be
like Mandarin ducks in the water♪

44:19.260 --> 44:21.390
